										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The digital age is evolving at lightspeed, and staying apace requires a special kind of savvy‚Äî especially for those in the throes of marketing. Artificial intelligence (AI) has stepped out of a sci-fi movie and into our daily communications, specifically in the world of social media. Marketers must now utilize AI to streamline their strategies and deliver their messages effectively for brand awareness.</p>
<p>Below, we‚Äôll look closer at AI prompts that drive engagement on platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn and how they‚Äôre revolutionizing the approach to social media content.</p>
